    • toString

      public String toString()
      Returns a string representation of this mapping.

      For example, the mapping

      Example
      source 0 1 2
      target -1 3 2
      Example
      target 0 1 2 3
      source -1 -1 2 1

      is represented by the string "[1:3, 2:2]".

      This method relies upon the optional method Mapping.iterator().
